OL,3,CTrump brands Iran's leaders 'lunatics'
OL,4,Cafter attacks on US warships in strait
OL,6,FIran's leadership has been branded
OL,7,F"lunatics" by Donald Trump after three
OL,8,FUS destroyers were targeted by
OL,9,Fmissiles, drones and small boats in
OL,10,Fthe Strait of Hormuz.
OL,12,FThe US military said the "unprovoked"
OL,13,Fattacks were successfully intercepted
OL,14,Fand none of the warships were hit.
OL,16,FIn response, strikes were carried out
OL,17,Fagainst the "Iranian military
OL,18,Ffacilities responsible", including
OL,19,Flaunch sites and command and control
OL,20,Fcentres.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@JO]tD@ZOUtD@eO]yD@MOUzD@WO]
