OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1778263866
OL,3,CTrump brands Iran's leaders 'lunatics'
OL,4,Cafter attacks on US warships in strait
OL,6,FUS headquarters said it did not seek
OL,7,Fescalation but "remains positioned and
OL,8,Fready to protect American forces".
OL,10,FFollowing the exchange, Mr Trump
OL,11,Fwarned Tehran that the US would "knock
OL,12,Fthem out a lot harder, and a lot more
OL,13,Fviolently" if they did not sign a deal
OL,14,Fto end the conflict "fast".
OL,16,FIranian state media said the country's
OL,17,Farmed forces had exchanged fire with
OL,18,F"the enemy" on Qeshm Island in the
OL,19,FStrait of Hormuz, while explosions
OL,20,Fwere also reported elsewhere.
