OL,3,CTrump brands Iran's leaders 'lunatics'
OL,4,Cafter attacks on US warships in strait
OL,6,FThe latest confrontation underscores
OL,7,Fhow the waterway has become a
OL,8,Fflashpoint for the shaky ceasefire in
OL,9,Fthe two-month conflict.
OL,11,FWriting on his Truth Social platform,
OL,12,Fthe US president said: "Three World
OL,13,FClass American Destroyers just
OL,14,Ftransited, very successfully, out of
OL,15,Fthe Strait of Hormuz, under fire.
OL,26,@tD@XOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
