CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1778263866
OL,3,CTrump brands Iran's leaders 'lunatics'
OL,4,Cafter attacks on US warships in strait
OL,6,F"There was no damage done to the three
OL,7,FDestroyers, but great damage done to
OL,8,Fthe Iranian attackers. They were
OL,9,Fcompletely destroyed along with
OL,10,Fnumerous small boats, which are being
OL,11,Fused to take the place of their fully
OL,12,Fdecapitated Navy."
OL,14,FHe added: "A normal Country would have
OL,15,Fallowed these Destroyers to pass, but
OL,16,FIran is not a normal Country.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@RO]vD@KOU
