CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1778263866
OL,3,CTrump brands Iran's leaders 'lunatics'
OL,4,Cafter attacks on US warships in strait
OL,6,F"They are led by LUNATICS, and if they
OL,7,Fhad the chance to use a Nuclear
OL,8,FWeapon, they would do it, without
OL,9,Fquestion ` But they'll never have that
OL,10,Fopportunity and, just like we knocked
OL,11,Fthem out again today, we'll knock them
OL,12,Fout a lot harder, and a lot more
OL,13,Fviolently, in the future, if they
OL,14,Fdon't get their Deal signed, FAST!"
OL,16,FIt comes after the US proposed an
OL,17,Finterim plan aimed at ending the war,
OL,18,Falthough it is understood to leave the
OL,19,Fmost contentious issues unresolved,
OL,20,Fincluding Iran's nuclear programme.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@cO]
