OL,3,CTrump brands Iran's leaders 'lunatics'
OL,4,Cafter attacks on US warships in strait
OL,6,FTehran has said it was reviewing the
OL,7,Fproposals.
OL,9,FPakistan, which has been mediating in
OL,10,Fthe conflict, said it expected an
OL,11,Fagreement soon.
OL,13,FThe country's prime minister Shehbaz
OL,14,FSharif said Islamabad remained in
OL,15,F"continuous contact with Iran and the
OL,16,FUnited States, day and night, to stop
OL,17,Fthe war and extend the ceasefire".
OL,26,@wD@AOUyD@aO]
