OL,3,CTrump brands Iran's leaders 'lunatics'
OL,4,Cafter attacks on US warships in strait
OL,6,FMeanwhile, the US and its Gulf allies
OL,7,Fare seeking backing at the United
OL,8,FNations for a resolution condemning
OL,9,FIran's stranglehold on the strait with
OL,10,Fthe threat of sanctions.
OL,12,FHowever, it faces being vetoed by
OL,13,FRussia and China.
OL,15,FThe sea route, which is a major supply
OL,16,Fline for oil and gas supplies, had
OL,17,Fbeen open prior to the US and Israel
OL,18,Flaunching strikes against Iran at the
OL,19,Fend of February.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
