OL,3,CTrump brands Iran's leaders 'lunatics'
OL,4,Cafter attacks on US warships in strait
OL,6,FIn retaliation, Tehran effectively
OL,7,Fclosed the shipping lane, sparking a
OL,8,Fglobal energy crisis that has seen
OL,9,Fprices rocket.
OL,11,FThis led the US to impose its own
OL,12,Fblockade of Iranian ports, leading to
OL,13,Fa stand-off.
OL,15,FThe president said this week he paused
OL,16,Fa separate, short-lived naval mission
OL,17,Fto reopen the strait to shipping
OL,18,Fbecause of the "great progress" being
OL,19,Fmade in the peace talks.
