OL,3,CTrump brands Iran's leaders 'lunatics'
OL,4,Cafter attacks on US warships in strait
OL,6,FBut it has since been reported Saudi
OL,7,FArabia opposed the operation and
OL,8,Frefused permission for US planes to
OL,9,Fuse its bases and airspace.
OL,11,FConcerns over future freedom of
OL,12,Fnavigation through the channel have
OL,13,Fbeen further fuelled after Iran has
OL,14,Fset up an agency to approve and tax
OL,15,Fvessels seeking to use it, according
OL,16,Fto a UK-headquartered shipping data
OL,17,Ffirm.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
