OL,3,CTrump brands Iran's leaders 'lunatics'
OL,4,Cafter attacks on US warships in strait
OL,6,FLloyd's List Intelligence said the
OL,7,FPersian Gulf Strait Authority was
OL,8,F"positioning itself as the only valid
OL,9,Fauthority to grant permission to ships
OL,10,Ftransiting the strait".
OL,12,FThe company said the agency had
OL,13,Femailed it an application form for
OL,14,Fships wanting passage.
OL,16,FIn view of the current diplomatic
OL,17,Fmoves, the creation of the body could
OL,18,Fbe a way to ratchet up pressure and
OL,19,Fsend a signal to Washington during the
OL,20,Fnegotiations.
